{"tid":1033243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"正妹「西勁臭」求診　醫師夾出保險套！男友怒問「沒有沒有不是我」","createTime":"2019-02-23T03:43:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-23T04:07:00.000Z","uid":72009,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b4654161acf01f07b2697c43ac9556b47eac83fc","tid":1033243,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T03:43:37.000Z","msg":"與另一半享受魚水之歡之餘也要注意安全！發現問題及早就醫檢查！<br />\n<br />\n婦產科醫師李偉浩在節目《醫師好辣》中分享一件誇張的醫療事件，一名長相亮麗的正妹在男友陪同下就診，她害羞表示「我的男朋友嫌我妹妹很髒」，她進一步解釋，原來是私密處分泌物過多異常，李偉浩用鴨嘴器幫她內診。<br />\n<br />\n結果一檢查，分泌物果然非常多，感染的樣子也看起來髒髒的，深入一點看，才發現有一個小塑膠袋在裡面，夾出來一看竟是一個保險套。<br />\n<br />\n結束後情侶大吵了一架，女病患衝去質問男友「為什麼把保險套留在我體內？」，男友否認「沒有沒有不是我」，反控女友「有沒有在外面亂搞？」，爭執到後來還要醫師評評理，還問有沒有辦法驗一下這個保險套，讓李偉浩哭笑不得。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/life/realtime/20190223/1522327/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flife%2Frealtime%2F20190223%2F1522327%2F&d=gMg1FBwAZA1XbJy1Uvmn1C1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=387d69a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flife%2Frealtime%2F20190223%2F1522327%2F&h=43684a5d\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/life/realtime/20190223/1522327/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e8a822b0b731e908e58387e6806b1849cf0e626","tid":1033243,"uid":39710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T03:45:38.000Z","msg":"嘩屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4794ed3cc47c025124f121360acec14225b21410","tid":1033243,"uid":25858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T03:46: